#

Mango Salsa

10 min
$5
60 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

FreshEasyQuickHealthy

Description

A refreshing and vibrant mango salsa perfect for dipping or as a topping!

Ingredients

  • mango: 2 ripe, diced
  • red onion: 1/2 small, finely chopped
  • red bell pepper: 1/2, diced
  • cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • jalape単o: 1, finely chopped (optional)
